title: Week 5 Studs & Duds + Knox Knox Jokes - Fantasy Football Podcast for 10/11
description:
The Fantasy Footballers are back with a new episode! On today’s fantasy football podcast, get a full recap of the biggest Studs & Duds of Week 5! Which players are the most worrisome for the rest of the season and could be potential landmines? Plus, Monday Punday and NFL injury updates. Manage your redraft, keeper, and dynasty fantasy football teams with the #1 fantasy football podcast -- Fantasy Football Podcast for October 11th, 2021.
